<ul><li><span class="ouvrage" id="Brion1955"><span class="ouvrage" id="Marcel_Brion1955"><a href="/wiki/Marcel_Brion" title="Marcel Brion">Marcel Brion</a>, «&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal;">Thomas Mann</cite>&#160;», <i><a href="/wiki/Revue_des_Deux_Mondes" title="Revue des Deux Mondes">La Revue des Deux mondes</a></i>,&#8206; <time>1955</time>, <abbr class="abbr" title="page(s)">p.</abbr>&#160;348-35 <small style="line-height:1em;">(<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.revuedesdeuxmondes.fr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/2b63344ba4f506f1f7d8d28c43c50ef3.pdf">lire en ligne</a>)</small><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Thomas+Mann&amp;rft.jtitle=La+Revue+des+Deux+mondes&amp;rft.aulast=Brion&amp;rft.aufirst=Marcel&amp;rft.date=1955&amp;rft.pages=348-35&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Ffr.wikipedia.org%3AThomas+Mann"></span></span></span></li>
