opedie/thomas-mann/"><i>Encyclopædia Universalis</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/thomas-mann"><i>Encyclopédie Treccani</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://frankfurter-personenlexikon.de/node/438"><i>Frankfurter Personenlexikon</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.enciclopedia.cat/EC-GEC-0039799.xml"><i>Gran Enciclopèdia Catalana</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ne.se/uppslagsverk/encyklopedi/lång/thomas-mann"><i>Swedish Nationalencyklopedin</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.munzinger.de/search/go/document.jsp?id=00000000153">Munzinger Archiv</a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://snl.no/Thomas_Mann"><i>Store norske leksikon</i></a></li>
